These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, comedy, mystery, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, reggae, house, jazz
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is the fan of jazz##1
3. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | satire | mystery | comedy | documentary   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | hip-hop     | house   | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, white, lavender
House: victorian, colonial, modern, craftsman
1. the person who likes lavender is the colonial house##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the modern house##1
5. the colonial house is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | white | lavender | fuchsia | light-blue    |
| House   | modern    | colonial      | victorian | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, zinnia, balloon-flower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, almond-milk, 7up
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person who growsorchid is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Flower         | orchid | balloon-flower | zinnia   | iris |
| Beverage   | tea   | almond-milk | 7up | fanta         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
House: art-deco, victorian, modern, wooden
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, azalea, daisy
1. the person who growsmarigold is the wooden house##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the victorian house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
4. the victorian house is on the right of the wooden house##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| House   | wooden | victorian | art-deco  | modern      |
| Flower         | marigold | daisy   | azalea | bellflower |

