.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, ritmeester, montecristo, fonseca
House: futuristic, cottage, art-deco, tower
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the tower house##1
4. the cottage house is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Cigar   | fonseca | montecristo | ritmeester | aristoff |
| House    | futuristic       | tower | art-deco | cottage     |

