.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, lily, sunflower, amaryllis
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, watermelon, lettuce, potato
1. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Flower   | amaryllis | sunflower | rose | lily |
| Food           | raspberry      | lettuce | potato | watermelon    |

