.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, chess, billiard, go
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, lemonade, fanta
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
2. the person playing go is on the far right##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Game   | billiard | chess | backgammon | go  |
| Beverage           | lemonade | iced-tea | fanta       | soy-milk |

