.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, cauliflower, apricot, cranberry
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, australian, indonesian, spanish
1. the spanish is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the spanish is the person eating cranberry##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the australian##1
5. the chinese is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Food         | apricot | spinach      | cauliflower | cranberry |
| Nationality   | chinese          | australian | indonesian     | spanish    |

