.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, green, chestnut, fuchsia
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, project-manager, doctor, software-developer
1. the software-developer is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the left of the security-guard##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
4. the project-manager is on the left of the doctor##1
5. the software-developer is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Color   | green    | chestnut       | azure | fuchsia   |
| Job     | project-manager | doctor | software-developer   | security-guard |

