.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, musician, pilot, entrepreneur
4 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, backgammon, poker
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the musician##1
2. the pilot is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Job    | bartender | pilot  | musician | entrepreneur |
| Game   | poker | backgammon | scrabble          | snooker    |

