.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
City: rome, venice, san-francisco, nizza
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, adventure, spy
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to venice is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| City      | san-francisco | venice  | rome | nizza |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | adventure | spy           | musical   |

