3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of soul##1
4. the havana-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Cigar   | alhambra | havana | aristoff | vegafina  |
| Music-Genre           | blues | dubstep      | reggae | soul |

