2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the italian is the person driving the train##1
4. the japanese is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality          | turkish | japanese  | italian  | spanish |
| Transport   | tram   | quad-bike | train | van   |

