.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, magic-tricks, collecting, card-games
There 4 different types of food: tomato, peas, papaya, lemon
1. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating peas##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games     | camping | magic-tricks |
| Food         | lemon | peas | tomato   | papaya   |

