.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, dog, turtle, snake
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, pakistani, american, australian
1. the australian is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the rat is the pakistani##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the american##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the australian is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Pet   | dog      | turtle | snake | rat |
| Nationality     | thai | australian    | american  | pakistani |

