.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, iced-tea, juice
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, bridge, canasta
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing bridge is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing whist##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage         | coffee | iced-tea | juice | tea |
| Game   | canasta     | bridge    | whist      | mah-jongg   |

