.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, light-blue, white, blood-red
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, romance, martial-arts, scientific
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes white##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Color   | blue | white | light-blue | blood-red   |
| Movie-Genre     | martial-arts  | action    | romance       | scientific |

 